page_10_text=The closest thing to real-life Redstone (though is IRL harvested for Mercury). It can drop §4Thermal Expansion Cinnabar§0 if installed, as well as §4Extra Utilities' Resonating Redstone Crystal§0. It can generate between §3Y=5§0 and §3Y=12§0.
